---
title: Teriyaki-Glazed Pork Patties with Celery Slaw
description: Here’s a fun idea for tonight’s dinner, burgers without the buns! Not convinced yet, well let’s fix that. These pork patties are
cooked in a delicious teriyaki sauce after being combined with both ginger and lemongrass. Don’t forget the pickled onion and
slaw, it wouldn’t be a reminiscent burger without them.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
